You are working on a psychology test / personality quiz template.

## Key Architecture Rules

1. `TypeNumber` (1–9) is an INTERNAL type system. NEVER display it to users.
2. Users only see: statement text, result title, tagline, description, strengths, challenges.
3. Scoring is Likert-based: each statement maps to a hidden `typeNumber`, users rate 1–4,
   scores are summed per type. See `src/lib/testLogic.ts` (decoupled from UI).
4. Test state lives in TestContext (context/TestContext.tsx) with sessionStorage persistence.
5. Personal data (name, phone) is SERVER-SIDE ONLY — never queried from the browser.

## File Responsibilities

- `src/data/questions.ts` - Likert statement bank with hidden `typeNumber` mappings
- `src/data/results.ts` - Result descriptions per type (user-facing content)
- `src/data/config.ts` - Test metadata (title, description, share text)
- `src/lib/testLogic.ts` - Score calculation logic (hidden from UI)
- `src/lib/db.ts` - Server-only Neon Postgres data access (optional DB)
- `src/lib/api.ts` - Client-side fetch helpers for the /api routes
- `src/lib/adminAuth.ts` - Server-only admin session (httpOnly cookie) helpers
- `src/context/TestContext.tsx` - Global test state management
- `src/components/test/` - Test-specific UI (IntroScreen, ParticipantForm, ...)
- `src/components/ui/` - Reusable UI primitives
- `src/app/api/` - Server route handlers (results, ranking, admin)

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 15 App Router + React 19 + TypeScript strict
- Tailwind CSS v4 with the `@theme` directive in `src/app/globals.css`
  (source of truth — there is NO `tailwind.config.ts`)
- Framer Motion for all animations
- Fonts via `next/font/google` — no fixed font (ships with Noto Sans KR placeholder)
- Optional Neon Postgres (server-side) for storage / sharing / admin

## Entry Flow (do not change the order)

Two steps, intro first:
1. `IntroScreen` - intro copy + single "시작하기" CTA, NO inputs.
2. `ParticipantForm` - name (required), phone (optional), and a REQUIRED
   privacy-consent checkbox. Never remove or pre-check consent; submit is
   disabled until name is filled AND consent is checked. The consent timestamp
   is stored as `participant-consented-at` (ISO) in sessionStorage.

## Coding Standards

- All components use "use client" when using hooks or interactivity
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Korean UI text, English code comments
- No inline styles - use Tailwind utilities
- Framer Motion for animations, not CSS transitions for interactive elements
- Never use emoji in UI - use Lucide React icons

## When Adding Statements / Types

- Each result type needs a comparable number of Likert statements so scores stay fair.
- Keep statements neutral - no obviously "better" answer.
- Adding a type: expand the `TypeNumber` union in `questions.ts`, add a full
  `ResultType` entry in `results.ts`, keep `compatibleWith` valid.

## Deployment: GitHub → Vercel
GitHub push → Vercel 자동 재배포.
- Storage → Neon 연동 시 `DATABASE_URL` 자동 주입 (DB는 선택사항).
- `ADMIN_PASSWORD`는 서버 전용 (절대 `NEXT_PUBLIC_` 금지). httpOnly 세션 쿠키로 관리자 인증.
- 테이블 SQL과 나머지 키는 `.env.example` 참고.

## SEO 설정
- sitemap.xml / robots.txt 자동 생성 (`src/app/sitemap.ts`, `src/app/robots.ts`)
- `.env.local`의 `GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION` → Google Search Console 인증
- `.env.local`의 `NAVER_SITE_VERIFICATION` → 네이버 서치어드바이저 인증
- `src/app/opengraph-image.tsx`가 동적 OG 이미지 자동 생성

## 도메인 연결 (가비아 → Cloudflare → Vercel)
1. 가비아 도메인 구매 → Cloudflare Add a Site → 네임서버 복사
2. 가비아 네임서버 변경 → Vercel Domains에 도메인 추가
3. Cloudflare DNS: CNAME `@` + `www` → Vercel CNAME (Proxy: DNS only)
4. `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL` 실제 도메인으로 변경 후 재배포
